replies.bodyText:
TimeoutException only has two constructors:
    public TimeoutException() 
    public TimeoutException(String message) 

Not really any way to add a cause or anything to it. That is a bit unfortunate though.  and I agree a stack trace would be very valuable.
Of course, we can always use extension since TimeoutException extends Exception , which does have a 'cause' variable.
